<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5428911>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Pisulinella? aucoini sp. nov. from Meilhan (Lower Miocene). A, broken specimen (apical whorls removed) showing (arrowed) the ridge inside the aperture (MNHN-PL15356B). B & C, holotype (MNHN-PL15355A). B, in apertural view; C in right lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5428911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

